These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Music-Genre: electronic, funk, gospel, hip-hop
Food: raspberry, spinach, kiwi, pomegranate
1. Food:pomegranate is on the left of Music-Genre:gospel##1
2. Music-Genre:electronic is on the left of Food:spinach##1
3. Music-Genre:hip-hop is in an odd position##4
4. Food:kiwi is on the left or right of Food:pomegranate##3
5. Music-Genre:electronic is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | funk | hip-hop | gospel |
| Food        | raspberry | spinach   | pomegranate | kiwi    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Color: purple, ivory, white, light-blue
Birthday: july, august, january, april
1. Color:ivory is on the left of Color:light-blue##1
2. Birthday:july is on the left of Birthday:january##1
3. Birthday:january is in an odd position##4
4. Birthday:july == Color:purple##1
5. Birthday:august is on the right of Birthday:january##1
6. Birthday:july == Color:purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Color   | white | purple  | ivory  | light-blue |
| Birthday   | april    | july | january | august    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Sport: surfing, badminton, soccer, skiing
Flower: zinnia, orchid, lily, balloon-flower
1. Sport:skiing is on the left or right of Flower:balloon-flower##3
2. Sport:soccer is in an even position##4
3. Flower:balloon-flower is on the left or right of Sport:badminton##3
4. Flower:balloon-flower is on the right of Flower:lily##1
5. Flower:zinnia is in an odd position##4
6. Sport:badminton is on the right of Sport:soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Sport          | skiing | soccer | badminton    | surfing      |
| Flower   | lily        | balloon-flower     | zinnia | orchid |

