.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
City: edinburgh, liverpool, paris, new-york
Beverage: 7up, juice, tea, hot-chocolate
1. City:liverpool is between Beverage:7up and Beverage:hot-chocolate##2
2. City:new-york is on the left of City:edinburgh##1
3. Beverage:tea is in an odd position##4
4. Beverage:juice is on the left of Beverage:hot-chocolate##1
5. Beverage:juice is on the right of City:edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| City         | new-york | edinburgh | liverpool | paris |
| Beverage   | tea       | 7up   | juice    | hot-chocolate  |

