4. Movie-Genre:western is on the right of Beverage:soy-milk##1
5. Movie-Genre:epic is between Movie-Genre:western and Movie-Genre:satire##2
6. Beverage:mirinda is in an odd position##4
7. Beverage:mirinda is between Movie-Genre:epic and Beverage:water##2
8. Movie-Genre:epic is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:satire##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
