2. Food:potato is on the right of Game:monopoly##1
3. Food:peach is between Food:potato and Game:backgammon##2
4. Game:monopoly is in an odd position##4
5. Food:peach is on the left or right of Food:potato##3
6. Game:domino is on the left or right of Food:apricot##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Game      | domino       | backgammon   | monopoly | billiard |
| Food   | lemon | apricot | peach        | potato    |

