2. House:ranch-style is in an even position##4
3. Music-Genre:rock == House:ranch-style##1
4. Music-Genre:folk is on the left or right of Music-Genre:rock##3
5. Music-Genre:rock is between Music-Genre:punk and Music-Genre:folk##2
6. House:gothic-revival is on the right of Music-Genre:punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| House         | cape-cod   | ranch-style | tower | gothic-revival    |
| Music-Genre   | folk | rock  | punk     | trance |

