2. Cigar:alhambra is on the left or right of Cigar:dannemann##3
3. Cigar:montecristo is on the far left or far right##3
4. Music-Genre:salsa is on the left of Music-Genre:classical##1
5. Music-Genre:classical is on the right of Cigar:dannemann##1
6. Music-Genre:salsa is in an even position##4
7. Music-Genre:indie == Cigar:vegafina##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Cigar   | montecristo | dannemann    | alhambra       | vegafina |
| Music-Genre       | blues  | salsa | classical | indie  |

