.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
City: berlin, san-francisco, miami, hannover
Flower: orchid, begonia, marigold, daisy
1. City:san-francisco is in an even position##4
2. City:san-francisco is on the left or right of Flower:orchid##3
3. Flower:begonia is between City:berlin and Flower:orchid##2
4. City:san-francisco is on the far left or far right##3
5. Flower:marigold is on the right of City:hannover##1
6. Flower:marigold is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| City         | berlin | miami   | hannover | san-francisco |
| Flower   | daisy          | begonia | orchid         | marigold  |

 